  <name>Flashcard</name>
  <summary>Lightweight cross-platform flashcard application</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Flashcard is a minimal yet feature-rich flashcard GUI application
      built with C and Raylib. Supports CSV data format for easy management
      and provides a clean, distraction-free learning interface.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Cross-platform (Linux/Windows)</li>
      <li>CSV-based card storage with escape sequence support</li>
      <li>Catppuccin Mocha color scheme</li>
      <li>Score tracking and shuffle modes</li>
      <li>Minimal dependencies (Raylib only)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <url type="homepage">https://github.com/ryopc/c-flashcard-gui</url>
